---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="OpenClaw Alt provides independent, honest comparisons of AI automation tools."
  canonicalUrl="https://openclawalts.com/about"
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 sm:py-20">

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display text-gray-100 mb-6">About OpenClaw Alt</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-dark max-w-none prose-headings:font-display prose-headings:text-gray-100 prose-a:text-emerald-400 hover:prose-a:text-emerald-300">

      <p>
        OpenClaw Alt provides independent, honest comparisons of AI automation tools. We research the tools, test what we can, and write up what we actually find — not what vendors want you to hear.
      </p>

      <p>
        We may earn a commission when you buy through our links. This never influences our editorial judgment. If a tool isn't worth recommending, we say so.
      </p>

      <h2>Why we built this</h2>

      <p>
        The AI automation space is moving fast and the marketing noise is deafening. Every tool claims to be the best, and most comparison sites are thinly veiled ad copy. We wanted something different: clear, direct comparisons written by people who actually care which tool you pick.
      </p>

      <h2>How we evaluate tools</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Pricing transparency</strong> — We list actual prices and flag when things are obscured.</li>
        <li><strong>Real use cases</strong> — We describe who each tool actually fits, not who vendors say it fits.</li>
        <li><strong>Honest tradeoffs</strong> — Every tool has a "the catch." We tell you what it is.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate relationships</h2>

      <p>
        When we link to a product, that link may be an affiliate link. If you sign up or buy through it, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. We only link to tools we'd genuinely recommend.
      </p>

      <p>
        For the full disclosure, see our <a href="/disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure page</a>.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
